<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM9.8">
<l>poṉpeṟṟā reḻilvētap putalvaṉaiyun tampiyaiyum pūvai pōlum</l>
<l>iṉpaṟṟā nuṇmaruṅkul melliyaleṉ marukiyaiyum vaṉattiṟ pōkki</l>
<l>niṉpaṟṟā niṉmakaṉmēṟ paḻiviḷaittiṭ ṭeṉṉaiyunīḷ vāṉiṟ pōkka</l>
<l>eṉpeṟṟāy kaikēcī yirunilatti liṉitāka virukkiṉ ṟāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Kaikeyī, what did you get by sending to the forest</l>
<l rend="indent">[my] Son who [learnt] the graceful Vedas from those who bear excellence,</l>
<l rend="indent">[His] younger brother, and my pūvai-flower-like Daughter-in-law of delicate build</l>
<l rend="indent">who has a slender waist, which [even] the lightning cannot compare with,</l>
<l rend="indent">by creating blame on your son who you are attached to, and</l>
<l rend="indent">by sending me too to high heaven?</l>
<l>You live happily on this vast earth!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
